Description: "Biscotti" firmware for Convoy S-series and C8 lights
  General-purpose clicky-switch light firmware with many runtime config options
  to customize the interface to individual preferences:
  - many different mode groups
  - mode memory, or not
  Default config fits on an attiny13.
  Single power channel only.
Button-Type: clicky
Memory: offtime, mem decay, configurable
MCU: attiny13, attiny25, attiny45, attiny85
Authors: ToyKeeper
Modes: battcheck, tactical strobe, bike flasher, config, SOS
Extras: mode groups, LVP
License: GPLv3
